      "para_id": "Q001971.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Ur-Ninurta , the shepherd , who provides Nibru with everything , the herdsman of Urim , the išib priest of Eridug with pure hands , the favourite en priest of Unug , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the spouse chosen by Inana ."
    }
  ],
